  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Boy
    Abstract Class that simulates and defines the attributes of Generalized Virtual World Boy.
    ChoosyGirl
    Class that defines the attributes of and simulates Virtual World Choosy Girl.
    Couple
    Class that defines the attributes of Virtual World Couple.

    Class that defines the attributes of and simulates Virtual World Desperate Girl.
    EssentialGift
    Class that defines the attributes of Virtual World Essential Gift.
    Geek
    Class that defines the attributes of and simulates Virtual World Geek Boy.
    GenerousBoy
    Class that defines the attributes of and simulates Virtual World Generous Boy.
    Gift
    Abstract Class that defines the attributes of Virtual World Generalized Gift.
    GiftSelector
    Abstract class which is base class of GiftSelectorOne and GiftSelectorTwo.
    GiftSelectorOne
    Class that defines the first Gift Selection Algorithm( specified in problem statement).
    GiftSelectorTwo
    Class that defines the second Gift Selection Algorithm( specified in problem statement).
    Girl
    Abstract Class that defines the attributes of Virtual World Generalized Girl.
    LIT2015021_Q8
    Solution to Q8.
    LuxuryGift
    Class that defines the attributes of Virtual World Luxury Gift.
    Miser
    Class that defines the attributes of and simulates Virtual World Miser Boy.
    NormalGirl
    Class that defines the attributes of and simulates Virtual World Normal Girl.
    Stats
    Class whose responsibility is to compute and print required data about couples according to problem statement.
    TestUtility
    This class is a dedicated Testing Utility which creates random girls, boys and gifts of every type and stores them in files "rand_girls.txt", "rand_boys.txt" and "rand_gifts.txt" respectively.
    UtilityGift
    Class that defines the attributes of Virtual World Utility Gift.
    VirtualWorld
    This class simulates the Virtual World in which there exist some girls, boys, couples and a variety of gifts.
